Simple Chic Wedding Guest Book with Photo – weddings Simple Chic Wedding Guest Book with Photo Have a promotion during this period Simple Chic Wedding Guest Book with Photo quality productsThis wedding guest book features a simply chic modern minimalist design. It features your favorite photo on the front with ‘WEDDING GUEST BOOK’ above it and your names, date and wedding location below it. You can edit the WEDDING GUEST BOOK text above the photo to show a different message, or delete it without replacing it with anything, for a simpler look. While we’ve used all lower case for the sample names and location below the photo, you can of course use standard capitalization and use standard capitalization when you edit to show your own names, date and location. You might also choose to change the font or color of some text.. The default text color on the front and the spine is black. We’ve set the default background color as transparent on the front, back and spine to let the basic color of the guest book’s cover simply serve as the base. But you can change this and choose a color that suits your style. In that case you might well choose to edit to show that color over the entire surface, both front and back and the spine. We have left the back blank. Please don’t forget to edit the text on the book’s spine! It can be easy to overlook this. We’ve made the sample names and date there black, but you can change this color and of course you can change the nature of those details entirely-you might prefer to change the spine text to something like ‘OUR WEDDING GUEST BOOK’ or "BEST DAY EVER", etc. in a color of your choice, for example. Use the intuitive design tools, your favorite photo and your inspiration to make this simply stylish modern wedding guest book uniquely yours! Price:$51.57
